author: rickhall
msg: Modifies Felix' internal logger to track and use available log services
(FELIX-77). Also implements a new log level configuration property to
control how much information is logged by the framework.

author: vinoski
msg: The log4j logging level was hard-coded to WARN. This change picks up
the level from the amqj.logging.level property, so it can be varied
